                            <comment id="12957579" author="hadrian" created="Wed, 24 Nov 2010 04:57:08 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Sorry Willem, I didn&apos;t see that you assigned it to yourself.&lt;br/&gt;
Committed fix in r1038476 and improved support for Locale in camel-bindy.&lt;br/&gt;
Richard, thanks for taking the time to follow up on this.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="12957578" author="njiang" created="Wed, 24 Nov 2010 05:25:23 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;@Hadrian,&lt;br/&gt;
It&apos;s OK, all I did was removing the hard code of local.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="12957597" author="davsclaus" created="Wed, 24 Nov 2010 08:08:30 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Havent looked into if this is possible.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;I suggest that it should be possible to set a locale on the class annotation so all the fields etc. will default and use that locale.&lt;br/&gt;
It would be cumbersome to set locale on each field one by one if you just want to use the same locale.&lt;/p&gt;
</comment>
